ets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nLost in the cruel world (Mikasa 外傳)<br />\n<br />\n想重溫返漫畫但唔知係邊到睇起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#1-18: 托羅斯特區攻防戰<br />\n#19-33: 女巨編<br />\n#34-41: 塔戰<br />\n#42-50: 艾倫奪還戰<br />\n#51-72 王政編 (強烈建議動畫黨補返漫畫, 前面政變動畫改左好多, 兵長fans一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 後面地下教堂就冇乜分別)<br />\n#73-85 瑪利亞奪還戰<br />\n#86-90 世界真相編<br />\n#91~ &lt; 宜家第4季 (暫時漫畫最新係136話)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家經濟許可嘅話記得去買返套碟支持下 <a href=\"https://shingeki.tv/final/product/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshingeki.tv%2Ffinal%2Fproduct%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=e68faa57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shingeki.tv/final/product/</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直播link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/king_live_01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fking_live_01&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=10e6574a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/king_live_01</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://vaughn.live/sherming993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvaughn.live%2Fsherming993&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=82cc6c43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vaughn.live/sherming993</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://mov3.co/en/nhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Fen%2Fnhk%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=0dfc202b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mov3.co/en/nhk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.itver.cc/nhk-general-tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.itver.cc%2Fnhk-general-tv%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=c0bce6a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.itver.cc/nhk-general-tv/</a><br />\n<a href=\"htt